snippet: Coverage of the caucuses Tuesday night gave CNN an unusual second-place finish, but its 1.3 million viewer total was well below the 2.2 million total of four years ago.

headline.main: Fox News Leads in Iowa Ratings; CNN, in Second, Has Big Falloff
